  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK402">
<l>kallātāṉ coṟkā muṟutal mulaiyiraṇṭum</l>
<l>illātāḷ peṇkāmuṟ ṟaṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The desire of the unlearned to speak (in an assembly), is like a woman without breasts desiring (the enjoyment of ) woman-hood.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
